reviews.text: Parked my car yesterday and during daylight hours someone removed the catalytic converter from under my car. They must have raised the car and cut it off. Nightmare. Police notified. Waiting for the car park to contact me
Absolute ballcrap. Says every 15 minutes back yet over an hour and no sign of a bus wasting so much time of a day out. 0 stars if I could. F green travel,  just drive in.

Fantastic Station - Used Oxford Parkway for the 1st time.  - easy to get to & perfect for a family trip into London. Parking only £4 for all day I will be back again when I need to use it for business. Much better than main Oxford Station, Swindon, Bristol, Cheltenham, Gloucester.

I used the station for the first time last Wednesday and had excellent service from the staff!
I bought a ticket on Trainline that day and opted to use the app for my ticket instead of collect at station!!!
Big mistake! Anyway they were so helpful and called the company who in the end supplied the code to enable me to collect ticket! 
I was so grateful! Thank you both very much!
Debbie
That's how future train station should be built. Great spot and parking too.
